CASE

CASE

Usage: ^gCASE <target>^n

Quietly sizes up a target for pickpocketing without taking any action.
- Shows your estimated odds (your stealth vs. target awareness).
- Shows bystander count and a quick risk label.
- Use ^gPICKPOCKET <target>^n to attempt the lift.

^WTip:^n Odds improve if you're sneaking, dim, or less visible; crowds increase risk.
^WSee also:^n PICKPOCKET, STEAL, HEAT
